				<td colspan="2"><span>Klapton,
<br />

<br />
Thanks I've checked out most of the threads and the guides. Lots of info. to take in all at once but most of it makes sense. Some doesn't make sense at all (until I get to those levels to use said bits of info.).
<br />

<br />
One of the threads I was hoping to understand was the 'hotkeys' and twisting thread. The pics didn't show up (no doubt the thread is too old or something). So far what I've done to twist songs is have them mapped on my keyboard (I've a notebook so no numpad unfortunately). 
<br />

<br />
So I spend my time just clicking the mapped out songs on my keys. The only hotkeys I have are to switch instruments and weapons when need be. Since I'm new and soloing more than grouping I'm finding the kiting technique to work much better and faster than melee. Something to get used to I guess.
<br />

<br />
Thanks for the welcome and start. Lots to learn but having fun.
<br />

<br />
Cheers,</span></td>
